data.description:
One level living with the features and price you have been looking for.
Fabulous location in the Heart of the South Lake Minnetonka area. This one level living townhome is adjacent to the LRT Trail System.
The neighborhood is on the site of the original Gideon homestead and orchard.
Less than one mile from Excelsior, you can walk or bike into town in a few minutes. Minnetonka Marina gives boating access and is a quick stroll from the home.
Trail Runs west to Victoria and East to Minneapolis.
Two local restaurants, Hazelwood, and Joey Nova’s are across the street for your convenience.
The Gideon Woods Association is professionally managed with ample reserves and reasonable association fees.
This well-maintained home has had many recent updates including roof, HVAC, driveway, and more.
Be sure to see the video tour with aerials! You will see the charm and value in this hard-to-find property in South Lake Minnetonka!
